chairs.name: TY-B-01 Bar chair
chairs.description: Stylish bar stools specially designed for bars and high tables, with some models adjustable in height and 360-degree rotation, add a modern touch and comfortable experience to your home and commercial Spaces.
features: Ergonomic design provides comfortable support for the back
The surface of the high-grade fabric is skin-friendly, comfortable and easy to clean
High-density sponge filling ensures no collapse even after prolonged sitting
Stable and durable
